Dear Student and Respected Teachers,

The videos are useful to learn/teach CS concepts of GATE. If you have any doubts in any of the videos then, comment on YCLA Academy YouTube Channel or @YCLAAcademy Telegram Channel or comment section below.

  1. Digital Logic
  2. Programming and DS
  3. Algorithms
  4. Discrete Math
  5. DBMS
  6. Architecture and organization.
  7. Theory of Computation
  8. Operating System
  9. Computer Network
  10. Compilers
  11. Engg Math
